  <section class="bg-ds-white relative"><div class="mx-12 py-24"><div class="py-24"><h2 class="mx-auto text-center text-4xl font-semibold leading-[1.2] text-[#C6177C]">A Nix workflow that fits</h2><p class="mx-auto pt-4 text-center text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider text-slate-500 lg:max-w-xl lg:text-lg">Easily integrate Nix into your existing development process and deployment toolchain.</p></div><div class="mt-12 flex flex-col gap-8 md:flex-row lg:mx-auto lg:max-w-7xl"><div class="rounded-md border p-8"><h2 class="text-ds-night-sky text-4xl font-semibold lg:max-w-sm">Ship in a flash, no Bash</h2><p class="prose py-4 font-semibold tracking-wider text-slate-500">Deploy in seconds, not minutes. Skip the evaluation time, network bottlenecks, and scripting headache. Roll out updates with <code>fh apply</code>and be done with it.</p><img src="/_astro/deploy-with-fh.CWcdeXpo.svg?dpl=6a3ac6aa8f5f210009d64a75" alt="FlakeHub features diagram" loading="eager" decoding="async" width="890" height="315" class="w-auto pt-8 md:pt-28"></div><div class="rounded-md border p-8"><h2 class="text-ds-night-sky text-4xl font-semibold lg:max-w-sm">Ditch your “Nix bootstrap” scripts</h2><div class="prose py-4 font-semibold tracking-wider text-slate-500">Steps for a great Nix experience in your org:<ol><li>Install Determinate</li><li>There is no step two</li></ol>It works everywhere. Automatic garbage collection and enterprise certificates&mdash;all built right in.</div><img src="/_astro/ditch-bootstrap-scripts.BOTQIKAb.svg?dpl=6a3ac6aa8f5f210009d64a75" alt="FlakeHub features diagram" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="890" height="315" class="w-auto pt-8"></div></div><div class="mx-auto mt-12 rounded-md border p-8 lg:max-w-7xl"><div class="flex flex-col gap-14 md:flex-row"><div><h2 class="text-ds-night-sky text-4xl font-semibold lg:max-w-sm">Your cache and flakes wherever you go</h2><p class="prose py-4 font-semibold tracking-wider text-slate-500 lg:max-w-4xl">Log in from workstations, CI, and Amazon Web Services. <code>determinate-nixd login</code> and go. One command unlocks your team's caches and flake sources.</p></div><div><img src="/_astro/deploy-with-fh.CWcdeXpo.svg?dpl=6a3ac6aa8f5f210009d64a75" alt="FlakeHub features diagram" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="890" height="315" class="w-auto"></div></div></div><div class="mt-14 text-center"><div><a data-astro-prefetch="true" href="/nix-installer" class="text-sm font-bold transition-colors duration-hover md:text-base lg:text-lg inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-ds-magenta text-ds-white hover:bg-ds-sky-blue px-4 py-2 lg:px-6 lg:py-3"><span>Install Nix</span>
</a></div></div></div></section>
  <section class="bg-ds-white relative"><div class="mx-12 py-24"><div class="py-24"><h2 class="mx-auto text-center text-4xl font-semibold leading-[1.2] text-[#EF5E08]">The enterprise Nix distribution</h2><p class="mx-auto pt-4 text-center text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider text-slate-500 lg:max-w-xl lg:text-lg">From SOC2 compliance and Single Sign-on to fine-grained access controls and MDM-friendly automation, Determinate is Nix for your enterprise.</p></div><div class="mx-auto mt-12 flex flex-col flex-wrap justify-center gap-10 md:flex-row lg:max-w-6xl lg:gap-20"><div class="basis-2/5 rounded-md border p-4"><div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full border"><svg width="1em" height="1em" class="duration-hover hover:text-ds-magenta h-6 w-auto fill-white text-[#F06817] transition-colors" data-icon="heroicons:lock-closed"><symbol id="ai:heroicons:lock-closed" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M16.5 10.5V6.75a4.5 4.5 0 1 0-9 0v3.75m-.75 11.25h10.5a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25-2.25v-6.75a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25-2.25H6.75a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25 2.25v6.75a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25 2.25"/></symbol><use href="#ai:heroicons:lock-closed"></use>
      </svg></div><h2 class="text-ds-night-sky pb-3 pt-8 text-2xl font-semibold lg:max-w-sm">Secure, confident, reliable Nix</h2><p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider text-slate-500">Enterprise Nix that is secure, compliant, and dependable, reducing risks associated with open source and empowering teams to innovate fearlessly in critical environments.</p></div><div class="basis-2/5 rounded-md border p-4"><div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full border"><svg width="1em" height="1em" class="duration-hover hover:text-ds-magenta h-6 w-auto fill-white text-[#F06817] transition-colors" data-icon="heroicons:user-group"><symbol id="ai:heroicons:user-group" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M18 18.72a9.1 9.1 0 0 0 3.741-.479q.01-.12.01-.241a3 3 0 0 0-4.692-2.478m.94 3.197l.001.031q0 .337-.037.666A11.94 11.94 0 0 1 12 21c-2.17 0-4.207-.576-5.963-1.584A6 6 0 0 1 6 18.719m12 0a5.97 5.97 0 0 0-.941-3.197m0 0A6 6 0 0 0 12 12.75a6 6 0 0 0-5.058 2.772m0 0a3 3 0 0 0-4.681 2.72a9 9 0 0 0 3.74.477m.94-3.197a5.97 5.97 0 0 0-.94 3.197M15 6.75a3 3 0 1 1-6 0a3 3 0 0 1 6 0m6 3a2.25 2.25 0 1 1-4.5 0a2.25 2.25 0 0 1 4.5 0m-13.5 0a2.25 2.25 0 1 1-4.5 0a2.25 2.25 0 0 1 4.5 0"/></symbol><use href="#ai:heroicons:user-group"></use>
      </svg></div><h2 class="text-ds-night-sky pb-3 pt-8 text-2xl font-semibold lg:max-w-sm">Nix simplified, standardized, and scaled for the enterprise</h2><p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider text-slate-500">Scale consistent Nix configurations across the org, making best practices easy to follow, eliminating manual work, and enhancing developer satisfaction.</p></div><div class="basis-2/5 rounded-md border p-4"><div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full border"><svg width="1em" height="1em" class="duration-hover hover:text-ds-magenta h-6 w-auto fill-white text-[#F06817] transition-colors" data-icon="heroicons:star"><symbol id="ai:heroicons:star" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M11.48 3.499a.562.562 0 0 1 1.04 0l2.125 5.111a.56.56 0 0 0 .475.345l5.518.442c.499.04.701.663.321.988l-4.204 3.602a.56.56 0 0 0-.182.557l1.285 5.385a.562.562 0 0 1-.84.61l-4.725-2.885a.56.56 0 0 0-.586 0L6.982 20.54a.562.562 0 0 1-.84-.61l1.285-5.386a.56.56 0 0 0-.182-.557l-4.204-3.602a.562.562 0 0 1 .321-.988l5.518-.442a.56.56 0 0 0 .475-.345z"/></symbol><use href="#ai:heroicons:star"></use>
      </svg></div><h2 class="text-ds-night-sky pb-3 pt-8 text-2xl font-semibold lg:max-w-sm">Speed, efficiency, and reliability for Nix deployments</h2><p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider text-slate-500">Scale Nix configurations with consistency, minimizing manual work to empower teams, boost productivity, and improve developer satisfaction.</p></div><div class="basis-2/5 rounded-md border p-4"><div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full border"><svg width="1em" height="1em" class="duration-hover hover:text-ds-magenta h-6 w-auto fill-white text-[#F06817] transition-colors" data-icon="heroicons:computer-desktop"><symbol id="ai:heroicons:computer-desktop" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 17.25v1.007a3 3 0 0 1-.879 2.122L7.5 21h9l-.621-.621A3 3 0 0 1 15 18.257V17.25m6-12V15a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25 2.25H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 3 15V5.25m18 0A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 18.75 3H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 3 5.25m18 0V12a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25 2.25H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 3 12V5.25"/></symbol><use href="#ai:heroicons:computer-desktop"></use>
      </svg></div><h2 class="text-ds-night-sky pb-3 pt-8 text-2xl font-semibold lg:max-w-sm">Nix, say hello to macOS. Built for automation, easy by design.</h2><p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider text-slate-500">Unlock Nix on macOS, cloud, and dev machines with AWS and Mobile Device Management, cutting tech debt and easing oversight.</p></div></div><div class="mt-14 text-center"><a data-astro-prefetch="true" href="mailto:sales@determinate.systems" class="text-sm font-bold transition-colors duration-hover md:text-base lg:text-lg inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-ds-orange text-ds-white hover:bg-ds-magenta px-4 py-2 lg:px-6 lg:py-3"><span>Contact Us</span>
</a></div></div></section>

  <section class="bg-ds-night-sky text-ds-wisp isolate"><div class="flex flex-col gap-12 py-24"><h2 class="mx-auto text-3xl font-semibold leading-[1.2] md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl">Product overview</h2><p class="mx-auto max-w-lg text-center text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider lg:max-w-4xl lg:text-lg">Determinate Systems brings Nix to the enterprise with secure streamlined tools that simplify software development and deployment, enabling organizations to use Nix's flexibility with confidence, scalability and enterprise grade security</p><div class="mx-auto flex flex-col justify-center gap-12 md:gap-16 lg:max-w-3xl lg:flex-row lg:gap-20"><div class="flex flex-col gap-6 text-center"><div class="mx-auto h-40 w-64"><img src="/_astro/pink-bars.B_4TChwp.svg?dpl=6a3ac6aa8f5f210009d64a75" alt="Pink bars image" loading="eager" decoding="async" width="236" height="155" class="h-full w-full rounded-xl object-cover"></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-2"><h4><a href="/nix" class="duration-hover hover:text-ds-magenta text-lg font-bold">Determinate Nix</a></h4><p class="tracking-tight lg:text-lg">Stop fussing with the maintenance and just build</p></div></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-6 text-center"><div class="mx-auto h-40 w-64"><img src="/_astro/blue-bars.Dnm_TB4d.svg?dpl=6a3ac6aa8f5f210009d64a75" alt="Blue bars image" loading="eager" decoding="async" width="236" height="155" class="h-full w-full rounded-xl object-cover"></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-2"><h4><a href="/flakehub" class="duration-hover hover:text-ds-magenta text-lg font-bold">FlakeHub</a></h4><p class="tracking-tight lg:text-lg">Privately share and cache flakes across your team</p></div></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-6 text-center"><div class="mx-auto h-40 w-64"><img src="/_astro/orange-bars.B-YIR1h9.svg?dpl=6a3ac6aa8f5f210009d64a75" alt="Orange bars image" loading="eager" decoding="async" width="242" height="155" class="h-full w-full rounded-xl object-cover"></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-2"><h4><a href="/secure-packages" class="duration-hover hover:text-ds-magenta text-lg font-bold">Determinate Secure Packages</a></h4><p class="tracking-tight lg:text-lg">Secure, signed, auditable Nix packages that you can trust</p></div></div></div></div></section>

  <section class="relative bg-[#F1F1F1] py-[70px]"><p class="mx-auto max-w-sm pt-4 text-center text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider text-slate-500 lg:max-w-xl lg:text-lg">Testimonials from engineering leaders</p><h2 class="mx-auto pb-14 pt-4 text-center text-4xl font-semibold leading-[1.2] text-[#C6177C] lg:max-w-3xl">Nix success with Determinate Systems</h2><div><div class="mb-6 flex justify-center gap-2"><img src="/img/testimonials/yacine-hmito.png" alt="Avatar for Yacine Hmito" id="Yacine Hmito" class="avatar-img border-0 rounded-lg h-32 w-32" loading="lazy"><img src="/img/testimonials/mitchell-hashimoto.png" alt="Avatar for Mitchell Hashimoto" id="Mitchell Hashimoto" class="avatar-img border-2 border-amber-600 rounded-lg h-32 w-32" loading="lazy"><img src="/img/testimonials/jp.png" alt="Avatar for JP" id="JP" class="avatar-img border-0 rounded-lg h-32 w-32" loading="lazy"></div><div class="mx-auto flex justify-center"><div><div class="avatar-details mx-8 lg:mx-auto hidden" id="Yacine Hmito"><p class="prose text-ds-gray text-base font-light"><span class="text-ellipsis">The experience was super smooth.
